### ZapCloud API - Coleção de Testes
### Compatível com VS Code REST Client, IntelliJ HTTP Client e Insomnia
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Como usar: instale a extensão "REST Client" no VS Code
###            e clique em "Send Request" acima de cada bloco.

@base = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### ══════════════════════════════════════════════
### 1. HEALTH CHECK
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════

# @name health
GET {{base}}/health

###

### ══════════════════════════════════════════════
### 2. AUTENTICAÇÃO
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════

# @name register
POST {{base}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Lucas Dev",
  "email": "lucas@zapcloud.com",
  "password": "senha1234"
}

###

# @name login
POST {{base}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "lucas@zapcloud.com",
  "password": "senha1234"
}

###
# Salvar token: copie o accessToken da resposta do login e cole abaixo
@token = COLE_SEU_TOKEN_AQUI
@refreshTokenValue = COLE_SEU_REFRESH_TOKEN_AQUI

###

# @name me
GET {{base}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# @name refresh
POST {{base}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshTokenValue}}"
}

###

### ══════════════════════════════════════════════
### 3. EMBEDDED SIGNUP - Meta / WhatsApp
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════

# Passo 1: Gerar URL do popup de autorização
# @name authUrl
GET {{base}}/api/meta/auth-url
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# Passo 2: Callback (normalmente chamado pela Meta, mas pode testar manualmente)
# GET {{base}}/api/meta/callback?code=SEU_CODE&state=SEU_USER_ID

###

# Listar contas WABA vinculadas
# @name listAccounts
GET {{base}}/api/meta/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# Salvar o wabaAccountId da conta criada no Embedded Signup
@wabaAccountId = COLE_SEU_WABA_ACCOUNT_ID_AQUI

###

# Desconectar conta WABA
DELETE {{base}}/api/meta/accounts/{{wabaAccountId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ══════════════════════════════════════════════
### 4. CONTATOS
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════

# Criar / atualizar contato
# @name upsertContact
PUT {{base}}/api/whatsapp/{{wabaAccountId}}/contacts
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "phone": "5511999999999",
  "name": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@exemplo.com",
  "tags": ["cliente", "vip"]
}

###

# Listar contatos (com busca opcional)
# @name listContacts
GET {{base}}/api/whatsapp/{{wabaAccountId}}/contacts?page=1&limit=20&search=joão
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# Salvar o contactId
@contactId = COLE_SEU_CONTACT_ID_AQUI

###

# Buscar contato por ID (inclui últimas 20 mensagens)
# @name getContact
GET {{base}}/api/whatsapp/{{wabaAccountId}}/contacts/{{contactId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ══════════════════════════════════════════════
### 5. ENVIO DE MENSAGENS
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════

# Enviar mensagem de texto
# @name sendText
POST {{base}}/api/whatsapp/{{wabaAccountId}}/messages/text
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "to": "5511999999999",
  "message": "Olá! Esta é uma mensagem de teste do ZapCloud. 🚀"
}

###

# Enviar template
# @name sendTemplate
POST {{base}}/api/whatsapp/{{wabaAccountId}}/messages/template
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "to": "5511999999999",
  "templateName": "hello_world",
  "language": "pt_BR",
  "components": []
}

###

# Buscar histórico de mensagens de um contato
# @name getMessages
GET {{base}}/api/whatsapp/{{wabaAccountId}}/contacts/{{contactId}}/messages?page=1&limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ══════════════════════════════════════════════
### 6. WEBHOOK DA META (simulações)
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════

# Verificação do webhook (GET - feita pela Meta ao configurar)
# @name webhookVerify
GET {{base}}/api/whatsapp/webhook?hub.mode=subscribe&hub.verify_token=SEU_META_VERIFY_TOKEN&hub.challenge=CHALLENGE_STRING

###

# Simular mensagem recebida (POST - enviado pela Meta em tempo real)
# @name webhookInbound
POST {{base}}/api/whatsapp/webhook
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "object": "whatsapp_business_account",
  "entry": [
    {
      "id": "WABA_ID",
      "changes": [
        {
          "value": {
            "messaging_product": "whatsapp",
            "metadata": {
              "display_phone_number": "15550000000",
              "phone_number_id": "SEU_PHONE_NUMBER_ID"
            },
            "contacts": [
              {
                "profile": { "name": "João Cliente" },
                "wa_id": "5511999999999"
              }
            ],
            "messages": [
              {
                "from": "5511999999999",
                "id": "wamid.ABC123",
                "timestamp": "1700000000",
                "type": "text",
                "text": { "body": "Olá, preciso de ajuda!" }
              }
            ]
          },
          "field": "messages"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

###

# Simular atualização de status de mensagem
# @name webhookStatus
POST {{base}}/api/whatsapp/webhook
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "object": "whatsapp_business_account",
  "entry": [
    {
      "id": "WABA_ID",
      "changes": [
        {
          "value": {
            "messaging_product": "whatsapp",
            "metadata": {
              "display_phone_number": "15550000000",
              "phone_number_id": "SEU_PHONE_NUMBER_ID"
            },
            "statuses": [
              {
                "id": "wamid.ABC123",
                "status": "delivered",
                "timestamp": "1700000001",
                "recipient_id": "5511999999999"
              }
            ]
          },
          "field": "messages"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

###

### ══════════════════════════════════════════════
### 7. CENÁRIOS DE ERRO
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════

# Tentativa de acesso sem token
GET {{base}}/api/meta/accounts

###

# E-mail inválido no registro
POST {{base}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Teste",
  "email": "email-invalido",
  "password": "senha1234"
}

###

# Rota inexistente (404)
GET {{base}}/api/rota-que-nao-existe

###
